    1. What happens to microglia?\\
    \vspace{\baselineskip}
    2. Can this be studied in human-derived iPS cells?\\
    \vspace{\baselineskip}
    3. Given the high expression of these genes in peripheral blood, can we still study the relationship between their expression and neurodegeneration in human peripheral blood data?\\
    \vspace{\baselineskip}
    4. Will we eventually find evidence of variants (common or rare) in inflammatory genes which confer risk or protection from neurodegeneration?
